        <div class="about-text">
            <p>Welcome to Vernoquill, where words flow like ink from a quill. Our platform is designed for writers, readers, and anyone who appreciates the art of storytelling.</p>
            
            <p>Built with modern web technologies including Node.js, Express, and EJS, Vernoquill offers a clean, responsive, and user-friendly blogging experience. Whether you're sharing technical insights, creative writing, or personal thoughts, our platform provides the perfect canvas for your words.</p>
            
            <p>The name "Vernoquill" combines "vernal" (meaning fresh and new) with "quill" (the traditional writing instrument), symbolizing our commitment to bringing fresh perspectives through the timeless art of writing.</p>
        </div>

