                <li><strong>Express.js:</strong> Fast, minimalist web framework</li>
                <li><strong>EJS:</strong> Embedded JavaScript templating</li>
                <li><strong>CSS3:</strong> Modern styling and responsive design</li>
                <li><strong>Font Awesome:</strong> Beautiful icons</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

